(2, 106, 'Rob Beesley', 'rbeesley@financemyhome.com', '', '12.37.32.195', '2013-02-08 11:15:27', '2013-02-08 16:15:27', 'Great message Rick. Thank you!\n\nThought I would share the following from my son''s martial arts class last night. Many thanks to Sensei Rick Goss for sharing these and many other wonderful thoughts with our kids. \n\nThis day, I will accept all good things that are coming my way.  \n\nThis day is full of excitement, love, health, and prosperity.  \n\nThis day, people are calling on me to be of service to them and I respond by giving my very best.  \n\nThis day, I think and practice health in my life, refusing to accept anything less than perfect health.  \n\nThis day, I accept the abundance and prosperity that is mine and willingly share it with others.  \n\nThis day, I am in the present moment, and do not focus on past failures.  \n\nThis day, I spend in total enjoyment of what I do.  \n\nThis day, I fill with loving thoughts and actions toward all other people and myself.  \n\nThis day, I spend in grateful appreciation of all the blessings in my life.  \n\nThis day, this hour, this minute, this moment is all I have and I choose to use it in celebration!', 0, '1', '', '', 0, 0),
(3, 106, 'Peter Elsby', 'pelsby@remn.com', '', '23.24.137.21', '2013-02-08 15:27:39', '2013-02-08 20:27:39', 'There is no such thing as failure !! Stay positive , strong , stick to your integrity and you will have results and success.', 0, '1', '', '', 0, 0),
