(5, 106, 'Lisa Ristow', 'lisa@theristowgroup.com', 'http://www.LaughlinRadio.com', '74.32.82.245', '2013-02-11 14:04:29', '2013-02-11 19:04:29', 'Thank you to Frank Garay for sharing info on this blog in his newsletter! I love it because it is short, sweet and to a powerful point! I own and operate two businesses and balance the care of my special needs son. We all have our challenges and many reasons to be thankful at the same time. Today I''m thankful for you Rick! ~Lisa', 0, '1', '', '', 0, 0),
