(11, 106, 'Mark', 'mark.brown139@verizon.net', 'http://markbrown.valuedlender.com', '96.247.231.196', '2013-02-12 18:36:44', '2013-02-12 23:36:44', 'Start with positive affirmation from Day Timer/and attitude that today is going to be a "good day!"  End with at least 6 things written in the "Gratitude Journal."  \n\nSometimes 6 is tough to make.  Most days it''s way too few.', 0, '1', '', '', 0, 0),
(12, 106, 'Vickie Newman', 'vnewman@remn.com', 'http://www.remn.com/VickieNewman', '173.8.234.125', '2013-02-18 23:51:24', '2013-02-19 04:51:24', 'NEVER GIVE UP..ON SOMETHING YOU REALLY WANT.  HOWEVER IMPOSSIBLE THINGS MAY SEEM,THERE''S ALWAYS A WAY....\n\n There is inside you all of the potential\nTo be whatever you want to be \nAll of the resources to do\nWhatever you want to do.\nImagine yourself, as you would like to be,\nDoing what you want to do,\nAnd each day, take one step toward your dream\nAnd though at times it may seem too\nDifficult to continue; hold on to your dream.\nOne morning you will awake to find\nThat you are the person you dreamed of \nDoing what you wanted to do.\nSimply because you had the courage to\nBelieve in your potential\nAnd to hold on to your dream.', 0, '1', '', '', 0, 0),
