(545, 1, '2014-05-13 06:01:37', '2014-05-13 10:01:37', 'Have you ever wondered what it takes to be a ''top gun'' in life and in your business? Want to know the secret to exceeding expectations? If so, check out this week''s ''Chasing Excellence'' with Rick Floyd!\r\n\r\n<iframe src="//fast.wistia.net/embed/iframe/6nfn41960k?videoFoam=true" allowtransparency="true" frameborder="0" scrolling="no" class="wistia_embed" name="wistia_embed" allowfullscreen mozallowfullscreen webkitallowfullscreen oallowfullscreen msallowfullscreen width="640" height="360"></iframe><script src="//fast.wistia.net/assets/external/iframe-api-v1.js"></script>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://chasingexcellenceblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/Never_Fly_Solo_Rick_Floyd_Chasing_Excellence.jpg"><img class="alignleft  wp-image-547" alt="Never_Fly_Solo_Rick_Floyd_Chasing_Excellence" src="http://chasingexcellenceblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/Never_Fly_Solo_Rick_Floyd_Chasing_Excellence-202x300.jpg" width="164" height="243" /></a>Join Rick as he speaks with motivational keynote speaker, entrepreneur and salesman Rob "Waldo" Waldman. Lt. Col. Waldman learned all about exceeding expectations in the Air Force, and in this week''s video he offers Rick his unique perspective on chasing excellence.\r\n\r\nWaldo Waldman  The Wingman  is the author of the <em>New York Times</em> and <em>Wall Street Journal</em> bestseller <em><strong>Never Fly Solo.</strong></em>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nHave an awesome week!\r\n\r\nRick Floyd', 'Exceeding Expectations', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'exceeding-expectations', '', '', '2014-05-13 04:38:21', '2014-05-13 08:38:21', '', 0, 'http://chasingexcellenceblog.com/?p=545', 0, 'post', '', 1),
