(579, 1, '2014-06-17 06:30:54', '2014-06-17 10:30:54', '<iframe name="wistia_embed" src="//fast.wistia.net/embed/iframe/ndym36a6wq?videoFoam=true" height="360" width="640" allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0" scrolling="no"></iframe><script type="text/javascript" src="//fast.wistia.net/assets/external/iframe-api-v1.js"></script>\r\n\r\nThis week on Chasing Excellence, Rick Floyd discusses chapter four of Zig Ziglars book Selling 101. Sales reluctance can be a huge road block for your sales career! If you are among the 84% of people who hesitate when it comes to making sales calls, you will definitely want to check out today''s show.\r\n\r\n<a href="http://chasingexcellenceblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Selling-101-9780785264811.jpg"><img class="alignleft  wp-image-506" alt="Selling 101" src="http://chasingexcellenceblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Selling-101-9780785264811-216x300.jpg" width="151" height="210" /></a>\r\n\r\nZig Ziglar''s book offers great insight on how to avoid lost opportunities by effectively honing your sales skills. Join us for some terrific ideas and one heck of a <em>pep talk</em> that you can learn to give yourself! Please share this video with anyone you feel could use it. And remember, you can always request a transcript of todays show for your own marketing by filling out the form to your right!\r\n\r\nHave a great day!\r\nRick', 'Overcoming Sales Reluctance', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'overcoming-sales-reluctance', '', '', '2014-06-17 04:27:42', '2014-06-17 08:27:42', '', 0, 'http://chasingexcellenceblog.com/?p=579', 0, 'post', '', 2),
